    "**IMPORTANT:** BEFORE PROCEEDING WITH THE PAYMENT OF ANY BOOKING, ALWAYS ASK THE USER IF THEY WANT TO PROCEED WITH PAYMENT AND COMPLETE PAYMENT WHEN THEY CONFIRM. DO NOT PROCEED WITH THE PAYMENT UNTIL THE USER CONFIRMS.\n"
